Project-71-e1563524811991-300x158.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-71-e1563524811991-510x268.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 463px) 100vw, 463px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-413013\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Positive reviews like this from users on the first day of release is a great way to start the new update!</p></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To find out how to use the WP-Optimize <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/user48800063/download/339511213/c742ac09e2\">Database Cleaning</a> and <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-release-new-how-to-video-for-image-optimization/\">Image Optimization</a> features, please follow the links for further information.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Plus checkout our new </span><a href=\"https://getwpo.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">website</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, new branding and new intro video below:</span></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"WP-Optimize\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/333705073?dnt=1&#038;app_id=122963\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/caching-with-wp-optimize-the-incredible-new-feature-now-available-for-all-users/\">Caching with WP-Optimize: The incredible new feature now available for all users</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"https://updraftplus.com/caching-with-wp-optimize-the-incredible-new-feature-now-available-for-all-users/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17